data.description: Spacious 4 Bedroom, 3 Baths Home with Wood Floors is looking for those who Love To Cook & Entertain! AWESOME Updated, Eat-In Kitchen includes Cork Flooring, Quartz Counters. Oversized SS Fridge, Bev Fridge, SS Gas Stove w/6 burners, Built-In Microwave, Tall High-End Cabinets, Pantry, Recessed Lighting & Updated Pendant Lights & attractive Glass Backsplash. From the kitchen access a Spacious Covered Deck & Large, Level Fenced-In Backyard w/ Firepit & Storage Shed. Your choice; use Main Level Primary Bedroom Suite w/Gas Fireplace & Updated Bathroom w/ Quality Tile Shower or use as an Extra Family Room or Spacious Office. Keep one car off-street in the Garage & another on the Concrete Parking Pad.  Convenient location in a well maintained neighborhood. Close to Rosedale Beach Club. Newer windows, Security System, Roof, Furnace & Sink Disposal.
